title: SRBC, Fish Consumption Advisories for the Susquehanna River Basin, PA, 2006
name: SRBC, Fish Consumption Advisories for the Susquehanna River Basin, PA, 2006
description: Polyline shapefile representing streams in the Susquehanna River Basin that have a fish consumption advisory listing due to PCBs and/or mercury. These are advisories for eating sport fish. The New York State Department of Health (NYSDoH), the Maryland Department of the Environment (MDE), and the Pennsylvania Department of Environmental Protection (PADEP) issue these advisories on a yearly basis.
